This test will check that Sudoku can start a game in all levels.
<dl>
    <dt>Click on "very hard" to start a new game</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing a new Sudoku</dd>
    <dt>Now click on "Game" >> "New". Select a new game with level "hard"</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing a new Sudoku</dd> 
    <dt>Now click on "Game" >> "New". Select a new game with level "medium"</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing a new Sudoku</dd>
    <dt>Now click on "Game" >> "New". Select a new game with level "easy"</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing a new Sudoku</dd>
</dl>
This test will check that Sudoku can finish a game
<dl>
    <dt>Now click on "Game" >> "New". Select a new game with level "easy"</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing a new Sudoku</dd>
    <dt>Finish the game by solving the Sudoku. You can activate "Settings" >> "Show possible numbers" to finish faster</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing that you won the game</dd>
</dl>
This test will check that Sudoku can print a game
<dl>
    <dt>Now click on "Game" >> "New". Select a new game with level "medium"</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing a new Sudoku</dd>
    <dt>Select "Game" >> "Print..."</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing the printing dialogue</dd>
    <dt>Select the printer "Print to file" and select an output filename and directory (e.g. "sudoku_test.pdf" in your home directory). Click on "Print preview"</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing the preview of the Sudoku to be printed</dd>
    <dt>Click on the printer symbol</dt>
        <dd>The print preview window closes</dd>
    <dt>Open the printed file you just created</dt>
        <dd>The Sudoku appears in the file you just opened</dd>
</dl>
This test will check that Sudoku can run in fullscreen mode
<dl>
    <dt>Now click on "Game" >> "New". Select a new game with level "hard"</dt>
        <dd>A window appears showing a new Sudoku</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Settings" >> "Fullscreen"</dt>
        <dd> The sudoku is now running in full screen mode</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Settings" >> "Fullscreen"</dt>
        <dd> The sudoku is now running in window mode</dd>
</dl>

<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> 'failed' and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result</strong>